lymphocytes obtained from the spleens of the treated mice; d) AdTP increased the 
effects of 5-FU on lung metastases but failed to show any increase of life 
expectancy with any treatment performed. These data indicate that AdTP, although 
increasing some functional responses of lymphocytes in vitro, does not improve 
the therapeutic activity of cyclophosphamide, cisplatin, 5-FU and dacarbazine in 
the experimental models presently used.

