Isolation and Caenorhabditis elegans lifespan assay of flavonoids from onion.

Xue YL(1), Ahiko T, Miyakawa T, Amino H, Hu F, Furihata K, Kita K, Shirasawa T, 
Sawano Y, Tanokura M.

Author information:
(1)Department of Applied Biological Chemistry, Graduate School of Agricultural 
