Cost-effectiveness of point-of-care biomarker assessment for suspected 
myocardial infarction: the randomized assessment of treatment using panel Assay 
of cardiac markers (RATPAC) trial.

Fitzgerald P(1), Goodacre SW, Cross E, Dixon S.

Author information:
